Product name: Vintage New York city souvenir bracelet. Rockefeller Center, International Airport, Empire State Building, Coney Island, Statue of Liberty!
Description: This listing is for a Charming Vintage New York City Souvenir Bracelet.  Vacation, Tourist and old Landmark sites are the theme of the bracelet. The bracelet is gold toned with black hand set imported stones and the graphics are set off in a gold tone.  It is very well done and each plate is special, I enjoy the graphics of each one of them.  The middle plate features the Statue of Liberty surrounded by New York's very tall buildings at that time.  The Empire State building is the first plate dwarfing other buildings in the background.  Coney Island is the second plate, this one is my favorite! It depicts rides at the amusement park and is charming indeed! The fourth notes the International Airport, possibly JFK Airport today but I am not sure. The last plate features The Rockefeller Center.  The detail work is well done on each of the plates. The bracelet is in excellent vintage condition. It has never been removed from the original packaging card, The package says Highlights of New York, City of Wonders, Hand Set Imported Stones. It measures approximately 8 inches long, including the clasp and the charms are about 3/4". It belonged to my Great Aunt and I don't remember her traveling after 1970, I can't date it but would guess it was from the 1960's. Very classy and well done bracelet that would be a delight to own and wear for any New York City fan or resident!

Product name: Santa Hat for Dogs, Dog Santa Hat, Holiday Dog Hat, Christmas Hat for Dogs, Large Breed Dog Hat, Christmas Dog Hat, Santa Dog Hat
Description:
Looking for a cute pet photo prop for your Christmas pictures?  Or maybe a fun way to let your four legged friend join in on your holiday celebrations?  This traditional colored red and white Santa dog hat makes a perfect Christmas pet accessory - or gift!
But let's be realistic, most dogs don't enjoy wearing hats and shake them off almost immediately.  I took this into account and designed my own *nearly* wiggle proof pattern for this hat.  This unique design makes it much harder for dog to sneak his way out of it before you click the shutter.  And of course treats help too.
---- Wearing Instructions ----
My Santa hat design goes all the way around your dog's head, allowing it to stay securely in place with no pesky ties or straps.  Simply hold the hat with the white part facing you, then slip the hat over your dog's face and up to the forehead.  Gently fit your dog's ears into the ear holes, and you are ready to snap some adorable photos.
---- Measurements and Sizing ----
This hat was designed to fit large breed dogs, such as labradors and golden retrievers.  It fits most dogs up to about 60-70lbs with a head size of 18-20".  This standard hat size features a 5" forehead and 4" ear holes.
To measure your dog's head, measure all the way around your dog's head, in front of the ears.  For video instructions on how to take a measurement, you can visit:
http://www.aegeandrawn.com/measurements
If you need a custom size hat, you can request one here:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/476532278/custom-size-santa-hat-for-dogs-measure
---- Similar Items ----
Have another dog?  Want more accessories?  You might also enjoy some of my other pet hats and accessories:
https://www.etsy.com/shop/AegeanDrawn?section_id=17642908
The matching puffball scarf (designed to complete the outfit) can be found here:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/454208120/dog-scarf-christmas-scarf-for-dogs
---- Shipping Information -----
My items ship internationally from my smoke free, pet friendly home in Izmir, Turkey. I highly recommend allowing 1 month for delivery time, though most items arrive within 10-15 business days. This allows some room for any unexpected customs or holiday shipping delays.
Express shipping is available upon request for most items, but please message me advance as pricing varies on location.
If you have any questions about the product or shipping, please feel free to contact me.
Thanks!

Product name: Large Modern Design Dog House Plans - Print Version
Description:
Plans to build a beautiful dog house.
Please request plans to be emailed or sent to you in the mail.
I have updated my design to accommodate every dog breed. I have 4 different sizes.
Dimensions: 5'-0" x 3'-0" Large
I will send you my copyrighted high quality PDFs files and JPEG files with 100% accurate dimensions through your email for FREE. Or, I can print them on 8.5"x11" and ship them to you for 2.00 USD within the United States and around 3.00 USD everywhere else.
All of these are very accommodating doghouses. I made this dog house for my 4 year old Australian Shepherd, Savannah who weighs 65 pounds [Large size].
I have a blog with all of this information on it: 
http://doghousedesigner.wordpress.com/2008/07/30/modern-dog-house/
I drew these plans up on my computer using a program called "SketchUp." I put the work into them and just wanted to sell them and share my work.
It cost me about 80 total when all finished. Price included: wood, box of screws and corrugated metal. My money saving secret in building this was to go to Home Depot, Lowe’s or Menard’s. Find the scrap wood department and lay out your pieces on the floor. [Bring a tape measure and marker] Mark the cut lines, number the pieces [as I have drawn up in my drawings] and they will cut the wood right there for you. When finished, you just take the individually numbers pieces home and screw them together.
Using scrap wood or wood you have in your wood shop, saves LOTS of money!! This is a very quick and easy project and your dog will love you for it. This secret, saves you the mess and setup of your own, the improvement store will do it for you.
Each Dog House has drawings including:
Cover Sheet: Titled "Savannah Cabannah"
Page 1: Accurately numbered and dimensioned 2x4's
Page 2: Accurately dimensioned 1/4" plywood sheets [3 in total]
Page 3: Accurately dimensioned corrugated metal
Page 4: Complete layout of all materials needed to construction dog house
Page 5: Completely numbered construction sheet [Comparative to LEGO building instructions]
Page 6: Construction sheet [Comparative to LEGO building instructions]
Page 7: Construction sheet [Comparative to LEGO building instructions]
Page 8: Front and side elevation with dimension for final construction
I would love to hear back from those who have used my plans to build their doghouses. I will make a gallery once I receive your pictures. Please also leave feedback to let others know how our interaction went.
Please specify which you prefer, PDFs, JPEGs or actual printed 8.5"x11" pages.
Thanks for looking.
Please visit my blog at WordPress.com:
http://doghousedesigner.wordpress.com/2008/07/30/modern-dog-house/

More about our secret recipe ingredients:
Coconut oil-- is an amazing skin care ingredient.  Soothes eczema, sunburn and psoriasis, and has antiviral and antifungal properties. It is a powerful moisturizer that is beneficial to restoring dry or flaking skin. Coconut oil also helps to delay the occurrence of wrinkles due to its antioxidant properties, known to protect skin cells from damage over time.
Grapeseed oil—may reduce damage to skin cells and enhance the production of collagen and elastin which is important for strong and healthy skin.
Avocado Oil---the antioxidants in avocado oil, particularly vitamins A and E, can help soothe sunburned skin, may reduce itching and inflammation of the skin, and is also beneficial in softening rough, dry, cracked skin.  Avocado oil also contains sterolins, which are natural steroids. They may be effective in boosting collagen production and in treating age spots. 
Organic Sugar- a wonderful natural exfoliant that removes dead skin and cellular build-up, allowing fresh, rejuvenated skin to surface. It's use as a scrub will leave a beautiful glow to your skin, opening the pores of your skin to remove dirt, oils, and bacteria.
To Apply: Take a small quarter sized from the jar and gently massage into skin in desired area. Rinse with warm water and dry with a towel.  For best results, keep out of direct sunlight and keep at room temperature. This product comes in a glass jar so no toxic chemicals from plastic will leach into your product. 
As with any skin product always test a small area first to ensure no allergies.

Product name: Pink Glass Pipe/Smoking Accessories/Tobacco Accessories/Glass Pipes/Pipes/Glass Smoking Pipe/Glass Bowls/Pink Pipe/Glass Spoon/Girly Pipe
Description:
*This Glass Tobacco Pipe is made with Solid Transparent Pink Borosilicate Glass Tubing.
 Bottom of bowl is slightly flattened to help secure it from rolling of most surfaces and breaking.
*This Glass Tobacco Pipe is photographed with a Black and Colored Background so that you can see the full effect of what color it is. This Pipe is not a color changing pipe just solid Transparent Pink, which the Pink Color will darken after each use.
*This Glass Tobacco Pipe is available in sizes 3.25 inches up to 5 inches long and will fit safely inside your Tobacco Pipe Holder. 
NOTE TO BUYER:
This piece is designed for Tobacco Use Only. In order to purchase, You MUST be at least 18 Years old. It is your responsibility to check Your Local Laws in regards to the use of this product and Shipment of This Sale and Abide by them! If the buyer fails to do so, the Seller is NOT LIABLE! 
Material used to make this product include: Borosilicate Glass, Pink Glass Tubing, Clear Glass, Oxygen, Propane, Kiln, Flame, Fire, and Torch.
(Handmade in USA)
PROTECTING YOUR GLASS PIECE FROM BREAKING:
 Keeping your pipe stored in a case or pipe bag after it has cooled down and not in use is a great way to help prevent future breaks. :) 
 Try not to empty your ashes out by tapping your glass piece on a ashtray. I know a lot of people get in the habit of tapping their pipe on a ashtray which can cause small fractures in the glass and over time of it heating up and cooling down eventually can cause it to break.
 Using a poker or a pipe cleaner is a more cautious way of empting out and cleaning your pipe after use. ;)
Color Changing Glass Pipes:
In the early 1980’s glass artists began experimenting with silver and gold fuming processes in an effort to change the characteristics of Glass Pipes. What was discovered was that a thin layer of pure gold and/or silver applied to the inside or the outside of the glass pipe created a unique phenomenon once tobacco was introduced to the product. The tobacco particulate, combined with the precious metals refracted the light much like a prism, causing the pipe to change colors. Additionally, different tobaccos produced different hues insuring completely unique Glass Pipes based on individual usage.
Flavor Enhancing:
Glass tobacco pipes were developed to provide a pure smoking experience by eliminating the competing tastes of metal, wood and other porous or burnable materials, in effect isolating the natural flavor of the tobacco. Whether enjoying a beautiful Glass Hand Pipe, Bubbler or a Glass One Hitter you can be assured that glass will not impart any undesirable flavors or tastes. Solar Storm Creations Glass’s line of traditional tobacco accessories is designed specifically for the tobacco connoisseur.

Product name: Perpetual calendar - wooden perpetual calendar - wood calendar - Christmas gift - moon phase calendar - nature gift - gift for kids - home
Description:
Children thrive on rhythm. They also love to discover and learn. This calendar serves all those purposes. Every morning, visually describe how the day is unfolding and get a beautiful start... while also intuitively answering why the day is the way it is! At the end of the day, set the moon phase hand while gazing at the night sky and say good night to the day.
What sets this perpetual calendar apart?
=================================
It not only provides a beautiful place to organize all the information but it satisfies the inate urges of the child to always be curious and ask why. My daughter's favorite phrase is "but why?...". Well, here it is...
The season is autumn now. But why?....  Do you see the position of the Earth with respect to the Sun... This is where we live (point it out) and as we are moving away from the Sun... 
This calendar doesn't just say what, but also in a visual and intuitive way points to the "why". This gives an excellent starting point to encourage conversations about our Earth, the moon, weather, seasons and a lot more.
This beautiful wooden perpetual calendar doubles as a home decor!
Sections of this beautiful wooden calendar
=====================================
There are 6 sections to this perpetual calendar -
1) A temperature section. This sliding (magnetic) pointer sets the days' temperature and lets them choose their own clothing to dress for the day. When they set the pointer, it becomes much easier to persuade them to wear weather appropriate clothing (most of the time they make this decision themselves without prompting)
2) A hanging date section. By default this calendar comes with a chalkboard tile. You can write the date or draw something fun. Have a great picture of the activity you are going to do today? Switch the tile out and hand your picture! You also have the option of adding 16 two sided tiles with dates painted on them.
3) Weather section. Similar to the temperature section, helps them prepare for the day.
4) Days of the week section. 7 days wheel with a rotating hand to set the day. By default it is painted in rainbow colors. You can choose to leave it unpainted or rainbow colors or in Waldorf color of the days.
5) Moon phase wheel. Clearly depicts the Earth and the moon relationship and how the moon looks like in each phase and why.
6) Seasons and months section. Has the Sun and the Earth in 4 positions around the Sun, 4 seasons, season appropriate nature painted beautifully and the months engraved.
Size
=======
22" long, 9" wide and 0.5" deep. Yes it is a great sized calendar! 
********Note: The calendar will be trimmed off at the border, so there won't be the extra space outside border, if you want extra space, please let me know.*********
Materials
============
Maple. Beautiful hardwood maple. The rotating hands and the sliding pointers are cherry, giving a great contrast.
The details are engraved and painted using non-toxic water colors.
The calendar is finished with food grade linseed oil to bring the beauty of the wood.
Packaging
=========
This calendar comes beautifully wrapped in tissue paper and packed securely in a box, ready to be gifted. If you want me to add a gift note, please leave your note in the "notes to seller" section during checkout.i

Product name: Handcrafted redwood dreidels
Description:
About us:
I am excited to re-launch a family business,  We sell hand-crafted dreidels made from salvaged and scrap redwood.  Each letter is individually burned.  The dreidels are hand-sanded and sealed with non-toxic linseed oil and beeswax.  Variations in color and wood grain contribute to the beauty.  .  
I grew up in Berkeley, California and now live in Alameda, an island in the SF Bay.   My mom originally started this business in 1974, after searching high and low for something other than cheap plastic dreidels.   She enlisted some friends to help design, make and sell traditional wooden dreidels.
I have great memories of selling dreidels with my mom.   In addition to setting up shop at temple craft fairs around the Bay Area, she was a vendor on Telegraph Avenue in Berkeley – we would get up early, participate in the lottery for spaces, set up the booth.  In those days, many people didn’t know what a dreidel was, but my mom had a great sales pitch, and a knack for selling to people from all cultures.   My mom was a librarian at UC Berkeley, so she would frequently run into colleagues and friends.   (Side note -- Telegraph Avenue vendors would often trade their goods – which is how I ended up with most of my jewelry in high school, including liquid silver necklaces with turquoise or tiger’s eye.  And feather earrings, which apparently are back in style.)
As my mom and her partners became busier and busier with family and careers, the business became dormant.   
Still, whenever a friend happened to see one of the “first generation” dreidels, they would ask where I got it.   And I would tell the story of my mom and the Dreidel Factory, and explain that they weren’t for sale anymore. And after hearing myself tell the story over and over, year after year, I realized there was still a real interest in quality handmade dreidels.  So I decided to re-launch the family business (my day job is in biomedical informatics, using information science to analyze and process medical terminology for use in computer applications).  
I look forward to introducing our hand-crafted, locally-made product to a new generation.

Product name: Game of Thrones Birthday Invitation - Card - Scroll - Love Letter - Message - Announcement - Card - Anniversary - Raven
Description:
The perfect way to profess your love to the moon of your life, wish them a happy birthday, announce a surprise or just a special way to message your favorite Game of Thrones fan, this custom raven mail scroll is sure to be a treasured gift.  I will take your words and put them to paper that has been aged and burned at the edges by hand. Your message will then be scrolled,  sealed with wax using your choice of sigil (Targaryen, Stark or Hand of the King) and nestled in a bed of Spanish moss inside of a kraft gift box.  Your raven-post box will then be wrapped with a natural raffia ribbon and crowned with a single raven feather.  Scrolls are shipped via USPS first class mail....faster than a raven and much more trackable.  The golden dragon egg pictured in the listing can also be included as a keepsake for an additional 9.  Just select it at check out along with your choice of wax seal. 
**Please note that your scroll will be produced via printer using calligraphy font...they are not hand written.  You will thank me if you ever see my handwriting. 
HOW TO ORDER:
1.  Select your choice of wax sigil and add your raven post scroll to your shopping cart
2.  Add the text of your scroll to the "note to seller" box in your shopping cart.  Please be sure to proof your text.  I format your message to be scroll perfect but the words, spelling and punctuation are yours ...exactly as you send them to me.    
3.  The shipping address you enter for your order is where your message will be sent.  Be sure to list the recipient’s address if you’d like it sent directly to them.  
PROCESSING & SHIPPING:
Processing time is one to three rises of the sun.  Processing time does not include USPS shipping speed which is generally 2 to 5 days. Should you need your scroll to arrive swifter than swift, please contact me regarding upgrading your first class USPS service to priority 2 day mail.
EXPEDITED ORDERS:
Please send me a message via Etsy if you need your order to to ship faster than the processing time listed above. I am a huge GoT nerd that delights in making these scrolls so if I can expedite your scroll without cost, I am happy to do so at no additional charge.  Additional expedited mailing charges and/or rush fees may apply depending on my actual shipping cost.
FAQ:
1.	What are my message options?   
Your options are only limited by your own imagination…message text is 100% custom…you draft the text and I will produce it exactly as you’ve written it.  Please keep text to a maximum of 500 words.
2.	What size will my raven-post message be?  
Messages have a max measurement of  6.5” x 10”.  Your scroll will be sized for maximum aesthetic effect so size will be based on the number of characters you have in your message.
3.   How do I order multiple scrolls to be sent to different addresses?
You can place separate orders....1 for each ship to address.  OR you can place one order to be shipped to you and mail them to your recipients.
4.  Can I customize the scroll and/or box?
Yes, yes, yes!  I love customization requests....Etsy shoppers are incredibly creative....your ideas help my shop and my products evolve. Email me with your idea and I will do my best to make it happen.

Product name: Fab Foot Stretcher
Description:
The Fab Foot Stretcher was designed and is manufactured by Sage, a 13 year-old dancer. Dancers, gymnasts, figure skaters and swimmers know that flexibility and strengthening their arches is fundamental to correct positioning of their feet. 
Sage wanted to create a stretcher that not only gave her a consistently good stretch, but one that didn’t cause the heel pain that most stretchers do, was smaller in size, and of course she wanted it to reflect her personality by allowing her to choose what pattern she wanted; all while not paying the 60-100 that the majority of stretchers cost.
Sage met all of these goals and came away with a product that is able to achieve the same stretch as the 100 foot stretchers, more comfortably, and at a fraction of the cost! In fact, for less than the cost of one of the current choices of stretchers available, you could own two and stretch both feet at the same time! The Fab Foot Stretcher:
Is a specially designed arch stretcher made to increase flexibility in your arch.
Comes in many patterns
Has a wooden base and padded area for heel 
Includes a Theraband to increase stretch. 
Fab Foot Stretcher makes every effort to have each item shipped within 72 hours of order. Each is handmade at the time of your order by Sage, an 8th grader and dancer. So sometimes a math test or competition day comes first. Thanks for supporting her dreams and we wish the best for yours as well!
Always warm up foot before use and do not overuse. 
*Fab Foot Stretcher is not liable for any injury related to its use.

Product name: Marble maze - wooden marble run - special needs toy- portable marble toy - Christmas gift - gift for kids - montessori toys - marble race
Description:
A fun twist to the old fashion marble maze toy - reconfigurable marble maze. Want a toy that is open ended, provides endless hours of fun, develops fine motor skills and develops problem solving skills? This is it!
This marble maze is as easy as you'd like or as challenging as you can take! The tiles are removable and you can arrange it however you like. This maze is so much fun and so so relaxing! I find myself arranging and rearranging the tiles over and over again. It is hard to put down even for adults!
Size
==========
I have 2 options 16 tiles (4x4 tile arrangement) and 36 tiles (6x6 tile arrangement). Each tile is 1.5" square and each arrangement comes with its own tray. The size of the 4x4 arrangement including the tray is 7"x7", the size of the 6x6 arrangement including the tray is 10"x10".
 Comes with 3 colored 3/8" balls that are removable (colored red, yellow and green by default but can be customized to your choice).
MATERIALS
==============
These are made of hardwood maple (please note that the wood used to make the maze in the picture had some pretty dark sections. Usually, maple is buttery white and won't have the two tone shown in the picture). 
Each piece of the maze is sanded smooth for the safety of little hands. This wooden marble maze is finished using food grade linseed oil to bring the grain and the beauty of the wood. 
PACKAGING NOTES
====================
The maze will arrive in a wooden tray, neatly wrapped in tissue... ideal for storing, transporting and gifting. I will be happy to include a card or a note if you are sending it directly to the recipient. Just leave the note in the "note to seller" section or shoot me a message!
Recommended age : 6

Product name: Ukulele Strap- Adjustable neck style sling strap, Red, White tribal pattern woven trim, narrow width, hook attachment
Description:
This is an adjustable length sling style strap for ukuleles, guitarleles or any kind of "lele" or other small string instrument! No need for a strap button on the instrument! The ribbon is a narrow 3/4" inch wide  wonderful ikat woven ribbon.
This is a sort of cranberry red with white, blue and yellow details,  "X" tribal pattern on a black background. This strap is made from a modern, lightweight fabric trim and is a little more narrow than my other straps. Tribal style pattern shows on both sides very nicely, similar to my vintage guitar straps!
The strap is worn around the neck and has an adjustable plastic slide to control the length, and a secure plastic J hook at the end to slip into the sound hole of the instrument. A sling style neck strap will hold your instrument safely and won't damp the sound! Will not scratch or damage your instrument either- no metal parts, just soft fabric and a rounded plastic hook and slider.
**Definitely order the small size hook for soprano, and maybe concert sizes. Small hook will also work fine for larger sizes. Wide style hook is best for tenor or larger instruments. There is not enough clearance between the high string and sound hole on smaller instruments for the wide hook**
Average length fits most people, but let me know if you need something longer or shorter.

Product name: Ladies Claddagh Corrib Claddagh Wedding Band R126-S
Description:
Corrib Claddagh Band in Sterling Silver.
As Lough Corrib Spills out into Galway Bay along the Corrib river it passes the ancient village of Claddagh.It was here that the Original Claddagh Ring was first created by Richard Joyce in The 17th Century.
The history of the Claddagh ring dates back to the early 16th century, to the village of Claddagh in Co. Galway. Legend is that a fishing boat from the village was captured by pirates and the crew taken. Richard Joyce was to have been married that week but as one of the captured crew, he was sold into slavery where he learned the art of goldsmithing. He was released many years later and returned home to find the love of his heart. She too had waited for him and he made her a ring. The heart stands for love, the hands for friendship and the crown for loyalty. The Claddagh ring has become very popular all over the world, worn by all as a symbol of friendship, love and loyalty. Wearing the ring with the heart pointing away from your own heart denotes that you are "available" but worn with the heart pointing towards your own heart, means that you are "taken"!
The Corrib Claddagh brings new light to this ancient symbol of Love,Loyalty and Friendship. 
THIS RING IS: 6.5mm Wide
If you would like to order more than one ring size or metal choice in a particular design, the easiest way to proceed would be to order each ring separately. 
It is very important to choose the correct ring size when ordering, as each ring is custom made for you. In some cases, a ring with a continuous pattern is not re-sizable. If you choose the wrong size, we will be delighted to exchange your order for the correct size, but the exchange will be subject to a restocking fee.
If you are not sure of your finger size, the best suggestion we have is that you visit your local jewelry store to be professionally measured. Jewelers use steel ring sizers that come in narrow or wide widths. Keep in mind that the width of the ring you are ordering will affect what size you need - narrower rings will be a slightly smaller size than a wider ring on the same finger. This is especially important when ordering wedding rings or wide bands. In this case, make sure your jeweler uses his wider band sizers which are normally 6 mm or so in width. Remember also that your finger size is usually different for each hand, whatever hand you write with is probably a little larger. 
If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to Contact Us as we would be more than happy to assist!

Product name: Standard Turkish Spindle 3D Printed
Description:
The original 3D Printed Turkish Spindle!
7" shaft
5" arms
Each spindle has 2 arms and 1 shaft.  Mix and match colors for a truly personalized spindle.       
The "Glow White" is glow in the dark, it's a shiny pearly white.
The standard spindles weigh between 1.0 and 1.2 ounce.      
Spindles are made from PLA.  There is a heat warning.  You do not need to be worried about being outside or anything like that with PLA. Most PLA is stable to around 140 degrees (there may be slight variance due to different colors and materials) before it gets soft but a car can exceed these temperatures very quickly, even on cooler days the car can exceed 100 degrees inside. The seats and dashboards will be hotter yet from what I have read they typically run about 50 degrees hotter. On a sunny day your dashboard and seats can reach over 180 degrees. What we generally say is if it is comfortable for you, it is comfortable for your spindle.
**A NEW OPTION is to have a shaft molded from ABS.  These new shafts are smoother and stronger!  The final picture in the line up shows some of  the solid color choices I have.  This is subject to change and frequently does!  From left to right, they are; 
Yellow
Sparkle Red
Fluorescent Blue (out of stock)
Pink
Purple (out of stock)
Black
Green (out of stock)
Eggplant
Not shown but available are multis, which are a swirling mix of different colors.  
**The drop down menus allow you to choose PLA color choice and Shaft.  PLEASE INDICATE in the note to seller box if you want both arms the same PLA color or if you want different colors.  The Shaft option is for you to choose whether you want a printed from PLA shaft in the same color options as the arms shown above, or if you want a shaft molded from ABS plastic.  You can choose your own color from the ABS colors shown in the above picture or you can have me choose either one of those solids or a multi.
A typical note would be something like this;
Main arm candy apple red
second arm shiny neon green
Shaft PLA lemon yellow**
**If you are outside of the US, please note that once I send your package, it may take between 10 days and 2 months to arrive.  This is based on the actual times we have seen for past shipments.**

Notes:
- The month names are spaced for each letter to fit within a 1x1 grid box.
- The large box fit an entire grid box.
- The small check boxes are perfectly spaced to fit within the center of a 1x1 grid box.
- The calendars are spaced so that each number fits within a 1x1 grid box.
- *** Ink pad and clear acrylic block not included. ***
----------------
This calendar features my handwritten font that has been digitized and professionally manufactured in the USA.
These are high quality clear photopolymer stamps.
----------------
To Use:
- Select the calendar for the month that you want to stamp. Only ink the days for that month. 
Example: February 2017 with a Monday Start
  1. Select the stamp with "1 2 3 4 5" as the first row.
  2. Only ink numbers 1 - 28.  This can be accomplished using a stamp blotter or stamp marker.
  3. Stamp calendar onto journal.
  4. Ink the "M T W T F S S" and stamp onto journal.

Product name: Shiny silicone puffy heart resin mould
Description:
Super shiny puffy heart mould for use with resin. Each cavity is approximately 2 by 2 inches.
****Unfortunately I have had to raise the price of this mould as there has been a significant rise in the price I buy them for. My apologies but there is nothing I can do about this.*****
Photos of resin pieces to show scale and finish only.
I do not recommend using 10 minute resin with this mould as it is more corrosive than clear resin and may damage the silicone or fuse to it. 
Like any shiny mould this will dull with time after many uses, a simple polish of the final piece will return the shine.
Silicone moulds attract dust easily and leftover glitter may stick to them. Due to this I clean my moulds before every use by patting them with the sticky side of a piece of tape until they are super shiny and perfect again.

Product name: MASSAGE BAR Mold, 4 - 4.5 oz cavities, Silicone, TWH Exclusive
Description:
*This listing is for one mold. There are two molds in the picture just to show both sides. 
Massage Bar Mold Detail:
Each of the 4 cavities holds 4.5 oz of water to the rim. Filling it less full still gives a nice massage bar, but allows you to scale the bar size as you prefer between 3 oz and 4.5 oz. The cavities are 3 1/4" long, 2- 1/4" wide and 1 -3/4" deep. You can fill them as shallow as 1 -1/4" and still have a nice bar if you prefer a lighter weight product.
The massage nubs are sturdy, thick & properly tapered for easy unmolding. A cp soap recipe that is water discounted or contains sodium lactate is preferred for easy unmolding. You can also pop the mold into the freezer to firm up soft soap recipes before you unmold. You can use this mold for melt & pour & lotion bars as well. 
A video that shows unmolding soap made with the massage bar mold: 
https://youtu.be/fqzBVObQ8Uo
The mold die is embedded with our logo & website address & we had them made in our company color- turquoise! We are the only retailer that offers this mold. (Logo will not show on product- it's on the outside of the mold.)
Thank you! Happy soaping!

Product name: 37.5% OFF Crochet Pattern Bundle - 3 Sets of 3 Stacking Baskets - Crochet PDF Instant Download Instructions File by JaKiGu
Description:
Get all three of JaKiGu's  stacking crochet basket patterns from the Jute and Cotton Series at a 37.5% discount!
This crochet pattern bundle consists of three (3) separate PDF files: Round Jute and Cotton Stacking Baskets, Square Jute and Cotton Stacking Baskets, and Round Lace Jute and Cotton Stacking Baskets. 
JaKiGu crochet patterns are comprehensive (20, 25, and 20 pages respectively), and contain detailed instructions, illustrative photos, helpful tips, photo tutorials, and a summary of crochet skills needed for this project.
PATTERN OVERVIEW
These patterns are written in standard American terms. Collectively, they contain two non-standard stitches, which are explained in great detail both in words and pictures. 
SKILL LEVEL
Though I do not discourage anyone from attempting to crochet these baskets, the round pattern will be best suited for an intermediate crocheter with confidence crocheting basic crochet stitches, and with variety of materials. The square baskets pattern and the lace baskets patterns would be best suited for a very experieced crocheter. Ideally, this will not be your first crochet project. If you have never worked with jute before, please be prepared to be working with a fiber much stiffer and rougher than traditional crochet yarns.
MATERIALS
3-ply 3 mm jute; 4-ply, medium weight cotton*
5.5 mm and 11.5 mm hooks
*Specific brands, weights, and quantities of jute and cotton are included in each instructional booklet, as are the tips on finding the best alternatives if you can't source the suggested materials.

Medium ------Diameter: 22.5 cm (9 in) ----------Height: 9 cm (3-3/4 in)
Large ----------Diameter: 27.5 cm (11 in) ---------Height: 11.5 cm (4-1/2 in)
SQUARE (Pattern No 303)

Medium ------	20.5 cm (8-1/4 in) Square ------	Height: 9.5 cm (3-3/4 in)

MozzieToezzies are hand-made, soft sole shoes for babies and toddlers, created and crafted by me in Woodburn OR
Studies show that the best shoes for babies and toddlers when they are starting to stand and walk are the ones that mimic bare feet. Because of this, soft soled shoes are recommended by pediatricians and podiatrists. Soft soled shoes promote good balance, help develop the strength and grasping action of little toes, and allow for wiggle room and growth.

Description:
Seltene Knopfstiefel der Berliner Firma „Emma Bette, Bud und Lachmann“. In beiden Stiefelchen ist das Label der Firma angebracht. Die Firma hatte ihren Sitz in Berlin, W8, Leipziger Str. 31-32. Jeweils fünf originale Knöpfe zum Schließen. Exzellenter, ungetragener Erhaltungszustand. Die Dekoration ist nicht inbegriffen. 
Die Spuren der jüdischen Firma „Emma Bette, Bud und Lachmann“ verlieren sich in der Nazi-Zeit. Leider ist über das Schicksal von Emma Bette, Bud und Lachmann sowie der gleichnamigen Firma nichts bekannt. Wir können nur hoffen, dass ihnen die Emigration gelungen ist.
